    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight">Ready to Start Writing?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg mb-8 max-w-md mx-auto leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);">One simple purchase. No monthly fees. No cloud. Just a writing tool that's yours to keep — running right on your own computer.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="#" onclick="document.querySelector('#base-buy-btn').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'});return false;" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 px-9 py-5 rounded-xl bg-white text-[#2E6BB5] font-bold text-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all no-underline" style="text-decoration: none; box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);">
